high_descs: Go forward and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the bread on the counter.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Turn left and go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the bread on the counter, to the right of the butter knife.

high_descs: turn left to face the kitchen counters on your left
grab the bread off of the counter there
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the left side of the room
place the bread inside of the fridge, let it cool and then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the kitchen counter ahead
place the bread down on the kitchen counter top to the right of the butter knife

high_descs: Move to the stove and turn left to to face the counter.
Pick up the bread on the counter.
Turn around and bring the bread to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Bring chilled bread from the fridge to the counter right of the sink.
Put the chilled bread on the counter right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bread on the counter right of the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread and take it out again.
Turn left and approach the sink.
Put the bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward to the stove then turn to the counter on the left.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bread inside, close the fridge, wait a minute, then open the fridge and take the bread back out.
Turn to the left and go forward to the counter that is to the right of the sink.
Put the bread on the counter, just right of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on a counter.
